Package: mpi-start
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: MPI startup mechanism abstraction layer
 mpi-start is a set of scripts to close the gap between the workload
 management system of a Grid insfrastructure and the configuration of
 the nodes on which MPI applications are run. The package is used to
 help the user start MPI applications on heterogeneous Grid sites. 
 .
 Check the project home page at: http://github.com/IFCA/mpi-start
